<br>
I am all but a lowly 6th degree aspiring wizard from Erudin.  I need much guidance.  I am dirt poor, can barely afford to purchase my next set of spells.  I am trying to fish and bake to raise money.  Soon I will need to travel and find pelts for tailoring, and acquiring silk for trade.<br>
<br>
But I need wisdom and knowledge passed to me from the great lore keepers of our world.  Many times I have lashed out in angry and misused my magic for illgotten gains.  I do not want to be lost to the dark side, but sometimes I cannot help my actions.<br>
<br>
How incredible it would be if the citizens of Norrath knew that on such and such a night, at the old wizard spire in such and such a place, a great gathering of mystic wizards gathered for counsel and lore teaching, all in a great circle of power!<br>
<br>
Even a secret unknown Order of wizards would be great (maybe even better so others may moonlight with a public guild).<br>
<br>
